The paper discusses quality assurance in crowdsourcing, which is a topic that falls under the sub-category of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). The paper also introduces a novel crowd model and optimization algorithm, which are related to Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the importance of diversity and correlation of information within groups of individuals, which is related to Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) and Cybersecurity (cs.CY).
